headline: Here’s Why Western Digital and Seagate Technology Are Falling Fast Today
summary: FEATURE  Data-storage stocks were among the top-performing names in the last quarter, but they also took the hardest hit in Tuesday’s tech slump.   Seagate Technology Holdings was the biggest laggard in the index, falling 7.
